{
  "stem": "14168.1",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Also, from the cultural standpoint, it had a-- an opera company.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It had several theatres.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And there was a very active cultural life, musical life, in that city, up until the Nazis took power.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My family had not been from Breslau.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother's family, before my mother got married, moved from Upper Silesia to Breslau, around the turn of the century.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father was employed in Breslau.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was employed by a furrier.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Around 1906, he went to Breslau from Berlin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's where my parents met, about 1912, 1913.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My great-grandfather's name was Baer Yitzhak.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was great-great-grandfather.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was about 1810, 1800, around that time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was in 1812 that the Prussian Jews were emancipated and were made full citizens.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But they had to adopt secular names, if you will.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So Baer Isaac became Isaac Baer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my, and on my great-great-grandfather's tombstone is still the Hebrew word-- the Hebrew name-- of Baer Isaac.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And what were your parents' full names-- your mother's maiden name?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother's maiden name was Block-- B-L-O-C-K.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My-- her name was Marta Block.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She was-- she was born in Ratibor, in Upper Silesia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My father's family consisted of several brothers, and he had a sister, who-- all of whom were born in the province of Posen.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And while my father went to Berlin, they stayed there until the Poles took over.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I have a very loving memory of them, because I went to visit them every-- almost every summer.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They lived in a beautiful little town, where they-- nearby they had a field, they had an orchard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they had a general store.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had a-- we always enjoyed ourselves there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I also remember enjoy-- the joy of riding in their buggy.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
